I stuck with 1hs and 2hs for most of my Paladin's life.  Then they introduced 2hp (it's all 2hp, even if you have one of the rare 1hp weapons, it's counted as 2hp).  So, I decided to work that up.  Luckily, Centi Warspears came about around the same time.  One of the fastest piercers (with decent damage) available - and cheap, too.

When I was in my upper 50s, a Mace of the Fallen Crusader (1hb) fell in my lap (didn't realize how plentiful they were until afterwards).  Being a really nice 1hb, I trained it.  Luckily, I have shaman and enchanters who are my friend's.  With haste and grouping, I was able to get that 1hb up to max in no time (couple days, max).

My 2hb is still zero, and probably will stay zero.  I just don't have the patience to work it up.

