It's a pain in the butt, but on <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=962569">my SK</a> I try to round-robin on the different weapon skills.  I swap between Steel Rod of the Knight, Ornate Runed Blade, Centi Warspear, Mace of the Shattered Soul, and a Centi Shortsword. 

